<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://books.google.ca/books?id=DrIMlfGg2uoC" class="external text" title="http://books.google.ca/books?id=DrIMlfGg2uoC" rel="nofollow">Birley AR. Marcus Aurelius, a Biography. Routledge, 2000 ISBN 0415171253, 9780415171250 page 202</a></li>
