<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.jstor.org/pss/638194" class="external text" title="http://www.jstor.org/pss/638194" rel="nofollow">Kotrč RF. Critical Notes on Galen's De Venae Sectione Adversus Erasistrateos Romae Degentes [K XI 187-249</a> The Classical Quarterly, New Series, Vol. 23, No. 2 (Nov., 1973), pp. 369-374]</li>
